* :frt6Ca9539fzCnOL: The meditation idea of no-mind, no words, is an oversimplification. There is a spectrum of thought, from nonverbal to verbal to written, and it is all good. However it is a skill, learning what ideas deserve further attention, verbalization, calcification.
